data.description: Beautiful townhouse/condo with 3 levels fully finished. Conveniently located within minutes to Stone Bridge center, Potomac Mills Mall, Highway 95, Commuter lots, VRE and other major routes and not far from Washington DC. Freshly painted throughout. Updated kitchen with a lot of cabinets, granite counter tops and stainless-steel appliances. Breakfast room opens to a huge deck. Upper level offers 2 suites with their own private bathroom rooms. Primary bathroom offers double vanity sink and a massive walk-in standing shower. Fully finished lower level with a full-sized bedroom and attached 3rd bathroom. Completely turn key and ready for you to call it home This was the original one i got it from Truly amazing town house/condo with 3 levels fully finished.
